headline.main: Willkie Is in Egypt; Tired After Air Trip

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Sept. 2 -- Wendell L. Willkie stepped out of a plane onto the sun-baked Egyptian sand today to start his special mission to the Middle East, Russia, China and perhaps India.
